[name]
ISO-8859-1 encoding

[options]
encoding iso-8859-1

[input]
=encoding iso-8859-1

=head1 ACCENTS

Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!!

    Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
      Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!

Older versions didn't convert Beyoncé in verbatim.

[output]
.SH ACCENTS
.IX Header "ACCENTS"
Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!!
.PP
.Vb 3
\&    Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
\&      Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
\&        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
.Ve
.PP
Older versions didn't convert Beyoncé in verbatim.
